<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM3.4">
<l>uṇṭi yēyuṭai yēyukan tōṭumim</l>
<l>maṇṭa lattoṭuṅ kūṭuva tillaiyāṉ</l>
<l>aṇṭa vāṇa ṉaraṅkaṉvaṉ pēymulai</l>
<l>yuṇṭa vāyaṉṟaṉ ṉuṉmattaṉ kāṇmiṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There will be no associating, for me, with this orb[-like earth]</l>
<l rend="indent">that runs after food and clothes desiring [them].</l>
<l>See! I am the madman of the Him whose mouth sucked the breast of the mighty demoness,</l>
<l rend="indent">He of Raṅgam, He who resides in the [cosmic] egg.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
